snippet.title: Devil May Cry 4 Special Edition -- Launch Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
It's time to face your demons! Download  Devil May Cry 4 Special Edition today!

https://store.playstation.com/#!/games/devil-may-cry-4-special-edition/cid=UP0102-CUSA01671_00-MAINRDOBXXXX0000

Devil May Cry 4 Special Edition includes five unique playable characters, new modes, new costumes, and an unlimited amount of stylish action. Available now for download on PlayStation 4!

Rated Mature: Violence, Blood, Sexual Themes, Partial Nudity, Language
